Prep Time: 15 minutes
Cook Time: 20 minutes
Serves: 4

Ingredients:

White Radish (Muli/Daikon) – 1 1/2 pounds, peeled and shredded
Salt – to taste
Cilantro/Coriander – 5 sprigs, finely chopped
Green Chilies – to taste, finely chopped
Carom Seeds (Ajwain) – 1/4 tsp

For the dough:

Chapati Flour – 1 1/2 cups
Salt – 1/4 tsp
Oil – 1 Tbsp
Warm Water – 1/2 cup + 2 Tbsp

Extra Flour – for dusting
Oil – for pan frying

Method:
Mix_NNP Salt_NNP and_CC Oil_NNP with_IN Flour_NNP and_CC add_VB warm_JJ Water_NNP ._.
Knead_NNP to_TO form_VB semi-firm_JJ dough_NN ._.
