The_DT salt_NN will_MD pull_VB out_RP the_DT water_NN from_IN the_DT Radish_NNP ._.
Squeeze_VB out_RB and_CC discard_VB all_DT of_IN the_DT water_NN from_IN the_DT Radish_NNP ._.
Add_VB Cilantro_NNP ,_, Green_NNP Chilies_NNP and_CC Carom_NNP Seeds_NNS to_TO the_DT Radish_NNP ._.
Mix_NNP well_RB ._.
Divide_VB dough_NN into_IN approx_NN 8_CD balls_NNS ._.
Divide_VB Radish_JJ mixture_NN into_IN 8_CD portions_NNS ._.
